data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home, right in the middle of Highlands Ranch! A desired neighborhood, this home is close to excellent schools, parks and recreation centers literally right around the corner. It's perfect for anyone looking for an active and fun community filled with trails perfect for those sunset walks. Comes complete with a large back yard, a sitting room, large living room, finished basement and spacious bedrooms. Work for home? Awesome! Check out the loft that could be an office or even just a lounge area. Fenced back yard with large trees promises privacy. The home is complete with charming and bright wood floors as well as carpet. Worried about snow? Don't. This house is perfect for anyone who enjoys parks, trails and much more!
